      "step_type": "reasoning",
      "content": "- **Core scaffold:** amino acid\u2013like (tryptophan-like) framework: **\u03b1-amino acid** with an **indole** side chain.\n- **Key functional groups:**\n  - **Primary amine** at the \u03b1-carbon (**\u2013NH2**): typically **protonatable** (basic center).\n  - **Carboxylic acid** (**\u2013CO2H**): typically **deprotonated** at physiological pH.\n  - **Indole ring system** (fused bicyclic aromatic with **[nH]**): aromatic, lipophilic surface; indole N is **not basic** (pyrrolic).\n- **Structural alerts for CYP2D6 inhibition:**\n  - Has a **basic nitrogen**, but it is a **primary amine** adjacent to a **carboxylate** (zwitterion).\n  - Lacks classic **tertiary amine / quinidine-like** motif.",
      "tool_name": null,
